        {
            "title": "金管局：首季特定分類貸款比率升至1.98%　資產質素略轉差",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">金管局季報顯示，截至3月底，銀行體系特定分類貸款比率升至1.98%，按季回升0.02個百分點；需要關注貸款比率升至2.25%，上升0.1個百分點，連升3個季度。內地相關貸款的特定分類貸款比率跌0.1個百分點至2.27%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">首季零售銀行稅前經營溢利按年升15.8%，由於外匯及衍生工具業務收入、收費及佣金收入都升，但持有作交易的投資收入減少。淨息差1.51厘，按年收窄2個基點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">金管局表示，銀行體系維持穩健，資本及流動性充裕。首季資產質素略為轉差，但維持可控。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15046218-%e9%87%91%e7%ae%a1%e5%b1%80%ef%bc%9a%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e7%89%b9%e5%ae%9a%e5%88%86%e9%a1%9e%e8%b2%b8%e6%ac%be%e6%af%94%e7%8e%87%e5%8d%87%e8%87%b31-98%e3%80%80%e8%b3%87%e7%94%a2%e8%b3%aa%e7%b4%a0-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250622_CR_source_HKMA__02.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-27 18:01:00",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "港股午後尋底   金融股成跌市元兇",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股在期指結算日先升後回軟，金融股午後拖低大市，小米(01810)支持力量。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20240318_FI_source-ap_港股.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20240318_FI_source-ap_港股.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數午後跌破上午低位，低見24194，跌131點或0.54%，或暫時低位，現報    </p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數半日報5352點，升7點或0.14%，  </p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生國企指數半日報8777，跌26點或0.3%， </p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里健康(00241)升5.47%，報4.82元；小米(01810)撐市，貢獻恒指71點，YU7正式登場，股價升4.57%，報59.5元; 紫金礦業(02899)升4.92%，報20.65元 ; ，為暫時表現最好三藍籌</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新東方(09901)跌2.92%，報41.6元 ; 中國人壽(02628)跌2.97%，報18.96元 ; 藥明康德(02359)跌2.65%，報75.35元，為表現最差三藍籌股。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">金融股成跌市元兇，建設銀行 (00939)跌1.48%，報8元；工商銀行(01398)跌2.17%，報6.31元；滙控(00005)跌0.58%，報94.85元 ; 中國銀行(03988)跌2.11%，報4.64元 ; 招商銀行(03968)跌2.3%，報55.2元，幾隻股份合共拖低恒指68點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15045519-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e5%b0%8b%e5%ba%95-%e9%87%91%e8%9e%8d%e8%82%a1%e8%b7%8c%e5%b8%82%e5%85%83%e5%85%87",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-6.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-27 15:00:57",
